data.text:
New Vinyl Record - Tantric - Self Titled

Todd Whitener, Jesse Vest, and Matt Taul got fired from Days of the New, but they had the last laugh, forming Tantric and recording this self-titled, Gold-selling album in 2001 for Madonna's Maverick label with producer Toby Wright (Alice in Chains, Metallica, Korn) at the controls. Never before released on LP, this acoustic-tinged, grunge/nu metal classic emerges here in an orange vinyl pressing inside a jacket with inner sleeve. Limited to 1500 copies!
